{
  "stem": "8842.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He broke that on my back because it was hanging right in, in-- on a-- on a string. it was hanging like that on a-- he broke that.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Of course, they grabbed me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "My friends grabbed me and hardly, hardly walking on my own feet, we came back to camp.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And during the night I picked myself up a little bit and I said, if this was going to happen to me, I'm going to do that tomorrow again, but he's not going to catch me again.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sure enough, on the second morning, we woke up.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We walked out to the place.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I escaped again, and I came into a house, and I said to them, I'm hungry and I'm barefoot.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I cannot continue working to make the Germans happy.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Can you just help me with some food?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I'll do everything you want me into this house.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Just let me stay with you.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'll feed your cows and I'll feed your pigs and I'll wash your floors.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'll sew it for you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'll do anything.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Just let me stay with you.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they did, and I was working there a full day and every potato I threw into the cows or to the pigs, the second potato was in my mouth.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I filled myself up with so much of it, I cannot tell you how many, and packed my pockets full of them.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "By the time I had the evening, I had to go back, made sure, first of all, that the German will not see me, but I had even in my pockets some potatoes I could give my friends.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I did it every day for two weeks, and I build myself up.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I became the, the maid of this house.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
